name: ashutosh
text:
जकरबर्ग को सरकार के सामने गिड़गिड़ाना चाहिये पर मंत्री गिड़गिड़ा रहे है कि पीएम को गाली दी जा रही है ।

The biggest culprit is the TRP race. I have been demanding for a decade, rating of news channels should stop. It is creating an anti-debate society,

name: ashutosh
text: In such debates if one is not thick skinned, one can loose his or her nerve or blood pressure shooting. This i can say with my own experience. Why cant it be said TV anchors rightist/leftists/liberals are failing in their crafts if they cant do a saner debate. 1/4

name: ashutosh
text:
The debate gets worse if one disagrees on the issue
of nationalism, terrorism, Kashmir, minorotites/religious issues/riots. Constantly one is told in a very aggressive-intimidating language by a kind of panelists/Anchors, he or she is anti-national/traitors/internal enemises.1/3

text: without blaming anyone, this is time to ponder over the level of debate happening on TV, kind of language used by panelists, the kind of unrestrained liberty given by anchors to a kind of panelists and others are constantly heckled and accused with all kinds of bame calling.1/2
